    "Furthermore, it is important to highlight the ability of both DM-1c and DM-3c to break the deadlock of viscous intermittency by being able to reproduce the dip structure in the local scaling exponents, as shown in Fig. 5 in the range τ ≈ τ η.",
    "Fig. 6 shows how DM generation improves multiscale statistics as training progresses.",
    "We also evaluated another prominent generative model, the Wasserstein GAN, for this task.",
    "Despite efforts to train and select the best-performing model, its accuracy was only satisfactory at large and intermediate scales and failed considerably at smaller time scales.",
